  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Death and Ladders: Roll the dice, climb the ladders, avoid scythes, take risky shortcuts, use Tarot Ability Cards to improve your odds or trap your opponent. Reach the end first to win.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You are supposed to die, but Death is bored to death doing the same job for an eternity. So he gave you a chance to win back your life, if you entertain him by playing his board game.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Gamble your soul in a relaxing atmosphere amongst a Skeleton crew, or if you want more of a challenge, try your luck against other unfortunate souls in Online or Local PVP.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Core is Random:</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3425390/extras/1f0393afc0fb76b902ce99881796e03a.poster.avif?t=1742407706\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3425390/extras/1f0393afc0fb76b902ce99881796e03a.webm?t=1742407706\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3425390/extras/1f0393afc0fb76b902ce99881796e03a.mp4?t=1742407706\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The core of the game is rolling dice, with the goal of climbing to the top of the board.</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >If you end your turn at the start of a ladder, you climb to higher ground.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >If you end your turn at the top of a scythe, you go to it's bottom.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You can risk taking optional shortcuts, but if you don't roll exactly what you need, the turn will be wasted</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Tarot Cards Improve Your Odds:</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3425390/extras/ca81d46d8b6512f88ae6f743febf6313.poster.avif?t=1742407706\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3425390/extras/ca81d46d8b6512f88ae6f743febf6313.webm?t=1742407706\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3425390/extras/ca81d46d8b6512f88ae6f743febf6313.mp4?t=1742407706\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >At the start of each turn you will get a certain amount of Tarot Ability Cards.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use those cards to improve your odds, or trap your opponent.</p></li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Death and Ladders: Roll the dice, climb the ladders, avoid scythes, take risky shortcuts, use Tarot Ability Cards to improve your odds or trap your opponent. Reach the end first to win.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You are supposed to die, but Death is bored to death doing the same job for an eternity. So he gave you a chance to win back your life, if you entertain him by playing his board game.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Gamble your soul in a relaxing atmosphere amongst a Skeleton crew, or if you want more of a challenge, try your luck against other unfortunate souls in Online or Local PVP.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Core is Random:</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3425390/extras/1f0393afc0fb76b902ce99881796e03a.poster.avif?t=1742407706\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3425390/extras/1f0393afc0fb76b902ce99881796e03a.webm?t=1742407706\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3425390/extras/1f0393afc0fb76b902ce99881796e03a.mp4?t=1742407706\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The core of the game is rolling dice, with the goal of climbing to the top of the board.</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >If you end your turn at the start of a ladder, you climb to higher ground.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >If you end your turn at the top of a scythe, you go to it's bottom.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You can risk taking optional shortcuts, but if you don't roll exactly what you need, the turn will be wasted</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Tarot Cards Improve Your Odds:</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3425390/extras/ca81d46d8b6512f88ae6f743febf6313.poster.avif?t=1742407706\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3425390/extras/ca81d46d8b6512f88ae6f743febf6313.webm?t=1742407706\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3425390/extras/ca81d46d8b6512f88ae6f743febf6313.mp4?t=1742407706\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >At the start of each turn you will get a certain amount of Tarot Ability Cards.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use those cards to improve your odds, or trap your opponent.</p></li></ul>",
